# Personal Development Context (template)

# Copy this to CLAUDE.local.md and fill in your local paths.
# CLAUDE.local.md is gitignored and never committed.

## Vault Integration (optional)

# If you have the Obsidian vault, launch Claude Code with:
# CLAUDE_CODE_ADDITIONAL_DIRECTORIES_CLAUDE_MD=1
# Vault path: ~/Obsidian/obsidian

## Sibling Repo Paths

# Uncomment and set paths to sibling repos on your machine:
# - Reference pod: ~/path/to/cogitarelink-solid
# - Fabric nodes: ~/path/to/cogitarelink-fabric
# - RLM substrate: ~/path/to/rlm

## Reference Pod

# To run the reference pod for testing:
# cd /path/to/cogitarelink-solid && make up
# Pod URL: http://pod.vardeman.me:3000/vault/
# Requires: 127.0.0.1 pod.vardeman.me in /etc/hosts
